**`.lathe/falsify.sh`** — Claim 4 (no unsafe) via grep, Claim 1 (build/clippy) via cargo, Claim 3 (token size) via one `--lib` test, Claim 5 (runtime codegen) via one `--test e2e` assembly inspection, Claim 6 (adversarial CLI) via constructed inputs. Skips Claim 2 (full test suite) since snapshot.sh already runs it and it would double the cycle time.

